 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uzestrenocya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zestrenocya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Norrath's Finest Taxi Service</span><br>  Posts: 1132<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/13/01 6:37:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DISCUSSION - Our Reservation system</span><hr size=1> Answers from my personal opinion...<br>
