it would cut off some people reserving something and planning on other people to kill it for them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usadara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sadara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boo!!!</span><br>  Posts: 653<br> <font color=#CC9900>(4/14/01 1:07:03 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DISCUSSION - Our Reservation system</span><hr size=1> Venril - Yes, Venril should be reservable.  Yes, take Indy's off the list (right off the top that will shave 7 weeks off the list).  Yes, the raid crew should be able to provide 50% of a 5 group raid with memebers of their own guild that are level 50 or higher.  <br>
<br>
